These include the poem 'Wild nights - Wild nights!', which elaborates on the desire to spend wild nights with a loved one. 'Hope', another poem, personifies hope as a bird that sings ceaselessly in one's soul, in both good and bad times. Atlantic_2024.04.02.pdf.summary: The document titled 'The Cystic-Fibrosis Breakthrough That Changed Everything' chronicles a significant advancement in cystic fibrosis treatment that essentially extended the lifespan of patients. A treatment called Trikafta, introduced in 2019, proved revolutionary, granting patients hope and more years to live. The therapeutic experience, often referred to as the 'Purge,' is likened to the recovery stage of a severe cold.
